
● MOC markdown sync is now implemented. Here's what was done:

  ---
  Summary: MOC Markdown Sync Implementation

  What Was Added

  1. MOC Relationship Config (MOC_RELATIONSHIP_CONFIG)
  Maps YAML frontmatter fields to Neo4j relationship types:
  - contains.knowledge → CONTAINS_KNOWLEDGE → Ku
  - contains.paths → CONTAINS_PATH → Lp
  - contains.principles → CONTAINS_PRINCIPLE → Principle
  - contains.goals/tasks/habits/events/choices → respective relationships
  - recommends.habits/tasks/events → RECOMMENDS_* relationships
  - related_mocs → RELATED_TO_MOC → Moc

  2. MOC Ingestion Engine
  Added self.moc_engine = BulkIngestionEngine(driver, MapOfContent, "Moc")

  3. _parse_moc() Method
  Parses MOC markdown files with frontmatter like:
  ---
  moc: true
  uid: moc.python.fundamentals
  title: Python Fundamentals
  domain: tech
  contains:
    knowledge: ["ku.python.basics"]
    paths: ["lp.python.beginner"]
  recommends:
    habits: ["habit.coding.daily"]
  related_mocs: ["moc.programming.basics"]
  ---

  4. Updated sync_file() and sync_directory()
  - Automatically detects moc: true in frontmatter
  - Routes to appropriate handler (KU or MOC)
  - sync_directory separates files by type and bulk-ingests each type

  ---
  How to Use

  Create a markdown file in your vault:

  ---
  moc: true
  uid: moc.morning-routine
  title: Morning Routine
  domain: health
  user_uid: user:mike

  contains:
    knowledge: ["ku.mindfulness.basics", "ku.sleep.hygiene"]
    habits: ["habit.morning.meditation"]

  recommends:
    tasks: ["task.setup.meditation-space"]

  related_mocs: ["moc.wellness.daily"]
  ---

  # Morning Routine

  This MOC organizes my morning practice...

  Then sync:
  sync_service = MarkdownSyncService(driver, default_user_uid="user:mike")
  result = await sync_service.sync_file(Path("/path/to/morning-routine.md"))
  # Or sync entire directory
  result = await sync_service.sync_directory(Path("/vault/mocs/"))

  The sync creates:
  - (moc:Moc {uid: "moc.morning-routine", ...})
  - (moc)-[:CONTAINS_KNOWLEDGE]->(ku.mindfulness.basics)
  - (moc)-[:CONTAINS_HABIT]->(habit.morning.meditation)
  - (moc)-[:RECOMMENDS_TASK]->(task.setup.meditation-space)
  - (moc)-[:RELATED_TO_MOC]->(moc.wellness.daily)
